# Build artifacts — `make`/DKMS regenerate these per kernel; only source is tracked
# (ch341.c, ch341.h, Makefile, README.md). A committed .ko is kernel-specific and
# useless on any other kernel, so it is deliberately ignored.
driver/*.ko
driver/*.o
driver/*.mod
driver/*.mod.c
driver/*.mod.o
driver/*.a
driver/*.mk
driver/.*.cmd
driver/Module.symvers
driver/Module.markers
driver/modules.order
driver/modules.builtin*
driver/.tmp_versions/
